      <title>巴拿马运河一月份允许更多船舶通行，降雨缓解干旱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/panama-canal-to-allow-more-ship-traffic-in-january-as-rains-ease-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 11 月降雨量好于预期，几个月来因干旱而紧张的巴拿马运河将从 1 月开始增加每天通过的船只数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/panama-canal-to-allow-more-ship-traffic-in-january-as-rains-ease-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 23:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
